title: Supreme Court lets Texas use gerrymandered map that could give GOP 5 more House seats
description: The Supreme Court has cleared the way for a Texas congressional map that may help the GOP win five more U.S. House seats in the 2026 midterms. A lower court found the map is likely unconstitutional.
content:
The Supreme Court has cleared the way for Texas to use its new congressional map that could help Republicans win five more U.S. House seats in the 2026 midterm election.
